class="card card-featured"><h1 class="card-title">
Candy Store Website Examples - 5 Sites That Highlight the Sweet Life</h1><div
class="card-body"><div
class="card-text card-text-prebyline">Browse our collection of five website examples that feature a discussion of the pros and cons and standout features.</div><div
class="card-byline"><div
