alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site stands out from more traditional sites by using a hamburger menu. However, this is the best option for the large menu selection, including pages dedicated to holiday specials.</p><p>The site's cookie-cutter edging shows its best advantage on the desktop, while the large shopping cart icon draws attention to the online shopping function. Confirming our real-world tests, Google's PageSpeed Insights test awards this site an excellent performance rating of 90/100.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-lolly-kingdom-20240621-mobile.webp"
