<span>Toronto, Ontario, Canada</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Candy Catchers is an online candy store based in Canada that also offers gifts such as bags, teddy bears, and balloons. The site features bright, high-quality images of candy, some of which do have the feel of stock images and a fun shop-by-color option.</p><p>The quick links at the bottom of the page direct visitors to important information, including FAQs and contact information. A clear menu offers visitors the chance to browse the different categories but does not float with the customer while scrolling.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
