alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site makes great use of the available white space for easy legibility; however, the text block on the gallery page is almost too small for legibility. The branding remains constant throughout the site, with the logo featuring prominently on the contact page. The desktop site shows slow loading times on the gallery page, which has resulted in a performance score of 89/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-grifits-candy-20240621-mobile.webp"
